sentences.text:
She further claimed as follows:

&#8226; after a death threat received in April 2002 she fled Seoul and went to live in Wonji City where her relatives found her a job;

&#8226; after two years had elapsed she returned to Seoul to care for her sick mother; 

&#8226; in December 2004, she was assaulted by masked men and returned to Wonji City, where she continued to receive death threats;

&#8226; in July 2005, she decided to leave South Korea as she considered her safety was threatened because she was a union member who supported strikes.
